name: TickleDiffusion
description:
What is it?

TickleDiffusion is a model aimed at creating tickle act in your art. If you're a total noob at writing a prompt, this model will do everything for you, even with a one-word prompt. Works great with single-one male and female characters. Alas, this version does not work well with tickling feet. I'm going to make a version for foot tickling, too. SOON™. More examples can be found on my Twitter and Boosty.

How to use?

Trigger Words - tkl, tickling, torso grab, disembodied limb, pov hands...

I use Clip Skip: 2, ENSD: 31337, vae from NAI.

More prompt you can found in the attached images.

Why not LoRA?

I also have LoRAs for body and foot tickling that work great. This model is a demo version of my LoRA's features. I'm going to update it and develop it further, and it will be enough for a normal user. If you want to speed up LoRA's release on CivitAI, then please support me on Boosty. I hand-selected over a thousand images for the dataset, cropped and cleaned them of text and other garbage that would affect the final result.

Support me
